hes%2C%20social%20media%20theme%20pages%2C%20and%20a%20print-on-demand%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObstacles%2C%20such%20as%20low%20sales%20or%20high%20fulfillment%20costs%2C%20prompted%20him%20to%20shutter%20those%20businesses%2C%20forcing%20him%20to%20reassess%20his%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20from%20business%20model%20to%20business%20model%20and%20had%20doubts%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20am%20I%20just%20too%20optimistic%3F'%20But%20then%20again%2C%20I%20told%20myself%20I'll%20get%20learning%20experience%20out%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20might%20not%20make%20money%20right%20now%2C%20but%20with%20the%20skills%20that%20I'm%20building%20up%20over%20my%20first%20few%20business%20ventures%2C%20one%20day%20I%20guarantee%20they'll%20come%20in%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20true%20in%20early%202024%2C%20when%20he%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20Etsy.%20Unlike%20social%20media%2C%20where%20algorithms%20can%20be%20tricky%20to%20read%20and%20attracting%20customers%20may%20feel%20unpredictable%2C%20Sidhu%20believed%20Etsy%20held%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20platform%20with%20built-in%20traffic%20and%20potential%20organic%20traffic%2C%20so%20I%20started%20uploading%20listings%20slowly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223967%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Etsy%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6906864cc007ca8c27381512%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamik%20Sidhu%20sold%20apparel%20on%20Etsy%20in%202024.%3Cp%3EThomas%20Trutschel%2FPhotothek%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESidhu%20launched%20his%20apparel%20shop%20in%20January%2C%20but%20closed%20it%20down%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20my%20customers%20were%20happy%2C%20but%20the%20occasional%20customer%20would%20not%20receive%20their%20order%20or%20experience%20delayed%20shipping%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20really%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20that%20same%20time%2C%20in%20March%202024%2C%20Sidhu%20decided%20to%20try%20digital%20products.%20He%20said%20he%20used%20Signal%2C%20the%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%2C%20to%20create%20a%20networking%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20built%20a%20private%20paid%20Signal%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecommunity%20where%20I%20taught%20teens%20and%20young%20adults%20how%20to%20get%20started%20with%20e-commerce%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20main%20focus%20of%20the%20community%20was%20print%20on%20demand%2C%20and%20how%20to%20research%20niches%2C%20set%20up%20stores%2C%20learn%20from%20competitors%2C%20design%2C%20and%20fulfill%20products%20on%20platforms%20like%20Shopify.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20people%20could%20purchase%20an%20e-book%20with%20advice%20and%20tips%20for%20%2450%2C%20or%20enlist%20Sidhu's%20help%20in%20developing%20their%20company's%20branding%20for%20%24150.%20Sales%20for%20his%20digital%20products%20peaked%20in%20April%20before%20slowing%20down%20in%20May%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20close%20the%20group%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243e2ef8d-c350-4207-97f1-2d98c54180cf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlways%20stay%20consistent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20young%20entrepreneur%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20set%20of%20challenges%2C%20such%20as%20juggling%20school%20and%20business%20or%20not%20being%20old%20enough%20to%20access%20certain%20accounts.%20Sidhu%20said%20the%20key%20to%20success%20is%20finding%20stability%20within%20those%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20tip%20I%20would%20say%20is%20to%20pick%20one%20thing%20and%20stay%20consistent%20with%20it.%20Stay%20dedicated%2C%20stay%20disciplined%2C%20and%20have%20a%20schedule%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20diving%20into%20a%20new%20business%20venture%2C%20know%20exactly%20what%20you%20need%20to%20get%20done.%20Know%20your%20timelines.%20Be%20strict%20with%20yourself%20about%20those%20timelines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20persistent%20is%20also%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20adapt%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20challenges%20that%20come%20up%2C%20and%20there's%20always%20competition%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidhu%20said.%26quot%3BThere's%20always%20someone%20who%20has%2010%20times%20the%20amount%20of%20experience%20you%20do%2C%20who's%20double%20your%20age%2C%20and%20has%20been%20doing%20it%20for%20most%20of%20their%20life.%20You%20need%20to%20stay%20consistent.%20Otherwise%2C%20you%20don't%20stand%20a%20chance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-made-72000-after-investing-ai-stock-e-commerce-profits-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762118338000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69068407c007ca8c27381500%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-made-72000-after-investing-ai-stock-e-commerce-profits-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teenager%20told%20BI%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20feeling%26quot%3B%20about%20investing%20in%20tech%20companies%20in%202024.%20%26quot%3BI%20caught%20the%20AI%20wave%20at%20the%20perfect%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-made-72000-after-investing-ai-stock-e-commerce-profits-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hurricane%20Melissa%3A%20Aerial%20view%20of%20'ground%20zero'%20destruction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762116815000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co