insider.com%2Fwanted-to-be-young-mom-had-kids-later-in-life-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estart%20my%20family%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20avoid%20a%20similar%20situation%2C%20but%20I%20had%20big%20dreams.%20I%20moved%20from%20Texas%20to%20New%20York%20City%20to%20attend%20theater%20school.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20cast%20in%20a%20terrible%20Shakespeare%20play%20where%20I%20met%20David%2C%20a%20handsome%20British%20tennis%20coach%2C%20and%20we%20fell%20in%20love.%20We%20headed%20to%20Hollywood%2C%20where%20my%20screenwriting%20and%20novel%20career%20took%20off.%20Nine%20years%20later%2C%20David%20and%20I%20were%20married%2C%20and%20I%20got%20pregnant%20right%20away.%20At%2033%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20age%20to%20start%20our%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20I%20had%20a%20miscarriage.%20Then%2C%20after%20a%20year%20with%20no%20baby%20luck%2C%20we%20saw%20a%20fertility%20doctor.%20This%20resulted%20in%20another%20year%20of%20tests%20that%20culminated%20in%20my%20unexplained%20infertility%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2036%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsurance-fertility-ivf-costs-hsa-millennial-couple-infertility-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebegan%20IVF%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20had%20a%20few%20setbacks%20with%20another%20loss%20and%20COVID.%20We%20decided%20to%20undergo%20one%20more%20round%20of%20IVF%2C%20and%20then%20we'd%20reevaluate%20our%20next%20steps.%20To%20our%20surprise%2C%20our%20five-year%20fertility%20journey%20and%20that%20last%20embryo%20resulted%20in%20the%20surprise%20of%20a%20lifetime%3A%20Not%20one.%20Not%20two.%20But%20three%20babies.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarried-an-identical-triplet-ive-only-confused-them-once-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIdentical%20triplets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20was%2041%20when%20they%20were%20born.%20David%20was%2049.%20I'd%20been%20worried%20about%20being%20too%20