C%20we%20couldn't%20imagine%20a%20better%20setup%20for%20what%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20our%20next%20chapter.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbenefits-of-only-child-more-time-financial-relief-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWe're%20a%20family%20of%20three%20by%20choice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we%20both%20love%20what%20we%20do%3A%20I%20am%20a%20writer%20and%20college%20writing%20professor%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20is%20a%20computational%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-francisco-bay-area-misconceptions-silicon-valley-what-its-like-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBay%20Area%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20work%20opportunity%20for%20my%20husband.%20Last%20fall%2C%20nearing%20his%20project's%20completion%2C%20he%20found%20an%20amazing%20job%20back%20in%20New%20York.%20Soon%20after%2C%20I%20had%20one%20too.%20Our%20new%20work%20schedules%20had%20built-in%20flexibility%20which%20made%20the%20idea%20of%20raising%20an%20elementary%20school-aged%20kid%20in%20New%20York%20City%20feasible%2C%20at%20least%20it%20seemed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2c67437-9b42-4f13-925f-0ebd417aa919%5C%22%3EWe%20tried%20to%20work%20around%20our%20son's%20school%20hours%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20would%20work%20just%2010%20minutes%20from%20our%20son's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-from-elementary-teacher-how-to-prepare-kids-for-school-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eelementary%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20meant%20he%20could%20do%20morning%20drop%20offs%20and%20a%20weekly%20pickup.%20I%20requested%20early%20morning%20classes%20which%20allowed%20me%20to%20do%20pickups%20two%20afternoons%20a%20week%2C%20and%20I%20interviewed%20a%20part-time%20babysitter%20who%20could%20stay%20late%20once%20a%20week%20so%20we%20sneak%20in%20a%20regular%20date%20night.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20agreed%20to%20split%20childc