20align%20with%20work%20schedules.%20Between%20minimum%20days%2C%20winter%20breaks%2C%20and%20holidays%20that%20working%20caregivers%20don't%20usually%20have%20off%2C%20finding%20coverage%20during%20the%20school%20year%20can%20be%20stressful%2C%20especially%20when%20a%20challenge%20at%20work%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20maxing%20out%20our%20housing%20budget%20we%20couldn't%20afford%20more%20hours%20for%20our%20babysitter%20or%20another%20aftercare%20option.%20Sick%20days%20also%20posed%20a%20challenge.%20With%20his%20commute%20temporarily%20altered%2C%20my%20husband%20couldn't%20easily%20work%20from%20home%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20while%20I%20taught%20my%20classes%20and%20then%20head%20into%20work%20once%20I%20got%20home.%20Doing%20any%20classroom%20volunteering%20and%20transporting%20our%20son%20to%20any%20extracurriculars%20would%20also%20fall%20to%20me%20for%20at%20least%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e051a680-3d2d-4a79-a6ab-19284e8630be%5C%22%3EWe%20parent%20from%20opposite%20coasts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20we%20talked%20about%20the%20challenges%20we%20were%20aware%20of%2C%20the%20less%20confident%20we%20felt%20that%20we%20could%20both%20do%20a%20good%20job%20at%20work%20and%20parent%20well%20at%20home%20much%20less%20show%20up%20for%20one%20another%20as%20a%20couple.%20Ultimately%2C%20we%20decided%20that%20it%20was%20best%20for%20our%20family%20to%20work%20on%20opposite%20coasts%20for%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dad%20teaching%20son%20to%20cook%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f6902a1c1f80efbec5e981%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20husband%20flies%20to%20the%20Bay%20Area%20to%20see%20them.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20backed%20out%20of%20the%20lease%20and%20my%20husband%20found%20a%20cheaper%20housing%20arrangement.%