due%20to%20the%20invasion%20of%20non-native%20species%20like%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20creating%20a%20pure%20environment%2C%20growing%20only%20what%20nature%20intended%20for%20in%20this%20particular%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20chasing%20what%20we%20saw%20in%20that%20movie%20Avatar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20reconnect%20with%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20acquiring%20the%20land%2C%20which%20was%20then%20covered%20in%20a%20eucalyptus%20forest%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-native%20species%20%E2%80%94%20the%20major%20challenge%20was%20rewilding%20it.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20land%20was%20used%20for%20agricultural%20purposes%2C%20it%20had%20been%20flattened%20and%20had%20some%205%2C000%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20These%20trees%20would%20dry%20up%20the%20groundwater%20and%20wetlands%20as%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20belong%20to%20this%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20biosphere%20was%20created%20through%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20of%20relentless%20effort.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-500x374.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-768x575.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-1536x1150.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.